problem is: All those=C2=A0<em>other=C2=A0</em>Bitcoin ETFs will charge=C2=
=A0<em><a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/33957045.25=
8408/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjQtMDEtMDkvZm=
91ci1iaXRjb2luLWV0Zi1ob3BlZnVscy1zbGFzaC1mZWVzLWJlZm9yZS1mdW5kcy1ldmVuLWxhd=
