and GBTC does have $29 billion of Bitcoins. And those Bitcoins have appreci=
ated<em>=C2=A0</em>in value: Most of them were put in the pot at considerab=
ly lower Bitcoin prices than today=E2=80=99s $46,000-ish, and Grayscale <a =
href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/33957045.258408/aHR0c=
